1
00:00:13,291 --> 00:00:15,083
[gasps]

2
00:00:25,291 --> 00:00:26,875
During the battle,

3
00:00:26,958 --> 00:00:30,000
I saw a young man
with short, black hair.

4
00:00:30,083 --> 00:00:31,916
That was Yuuto.

5
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:34,791
There was a very
peculiar reaction.

6
00:00:34,875 --> 00:00:38,125
The magics of Gleipnir
completely ensnared him.

7
00:00:38,208 --> 00:00:40,500
The reason your hidden magics
affected him in that way

8
00:00:40,583 --> 00:00:43,333
is because he was brought here
from another world.

9
00:00:43,416 --> 00:00:46,833
Oh! Another world, you say?

10
00:00:46,916 --> 00:00:48,500
What sort of mage
could have pulled off

11
00:00:48,583 --> 00:00:51,833
such a magnificent trick?

12
00:00:51,916 --> 00:00:54,583
Ah, but I bet you already
know the answer, don't you?

13
00:00:54,666 --> 00:00:57,500
Yes, it was my little
sister's doing.

14
00:00:57,583 --> 00:01:00,041
Well, isn't that something.

15
00:01:00,125 --> 00:01:02,000
He's quite the adversary.

16
00:01:02,083 --> 00:01:05,041
How are you going to deal
with such a handful?

17
00:01:05,125 --> 00:01:06,958
[LOPTR grunts]

18
00:02:38,125 --> 00:02:40,666
[YUUTO] "The Kotatsu
and the Empty Bellows."

19
00:02:43,875 --> 00:02:45,500
[YUUTO shudders]
It's cold!

20
00:02:45,583 --> 00:02:47,458
Winter really snuck up on us.

21
00:02:47,541 --> 00:02:51,125
I know, it feels as though it
could start snowing any second.

22
00:02:51,208 --> 00:02:53,166
[FELICIA gasps]

23
00:02:55,875 --> 00:02:58,083
Sorry you had to see that,
Big Brother--

24
00:02:58,166 --> 00:02:59,208
[YUUTO wails]

25
00:02:59,291 --> 00:03:01,083
I'm freezing!

26
00:03:01,166 --> 00:03:03,333
Come on, Felicia,
let's get going.

27
00:03:03,416 --> 00:03:04,583
[FELICIA gasps]

28
00:03:04,666 --> 00:03:06,250
Curses, and after I went
through all that trouble

29
00:03:06,333 --> 00:03:09,500
to make sure only
Big Brother could see it.

30
00:03:09,583 --> 00:03:10,958
[YUUTO]
Did you hear me?

31
00:03:11,041 --> 00:03:13,416
Why do you look so
angry all of a sudden?

32
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:14,625
[FELICIA gasps]

33
00:03:14,708 --> 00:03:15,666
Oh, no reason!

34
00:03:15,750 --> 00:03:17,916
It is rather chilly today.

35
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,833
Now would be the perfect
time to use that item

36
00:03:19,916 --> 00:03:21,458
I had setup in your office!

37
00:03:21,541 --> 00:03:23,958
And by "item," you mean?

38
00:03:24,041 --> 00:03:25,291
Ah!

39
00:03:27,791 --> 00:03:29,666
[sighs]

40
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:32,291
This kotatsu is exactly
what I needed.

41
00:03:32,375 --> 00:03:34,000
So warm and cozy.

42
00:03:34,083 --> 00:03:35,750
[YUUTO sighs]

43
00:03:35,833 --> 00:03:37,166
You don't have to stand there.

44
00:03:37,250 --> 00:03:40,000
You're more than welcome
to join me under the kotatsu.

45
00:03:40,083 --> 00:03:41,875
Are you sure
that would be okay?

46
00:03:41,958 --> 00:03:44,208
Yes, I had Ingrid make it
in the standard size,

47
00:03:44,291 --> 00:03:45,750
so there's plenty of room.

48
00:03:45,833 --> 00:03:48,208
It's too big for
just one person.

49
00:03:48,291 --> 00:03:51,166
Well then,
don't mind if I do.

50
00:03:53,583 --> 00:03:55,458
[sighs]

51
00:03:55,541 --> 00:03:57,375
This is wonderfully warm!

52
00:03:57,458 --> 00:03:58,708
I told you!

53
00:03:58,791 --> 00:04:00,875
And it doesn't use
any electricity.

54
00:04:00,958 --> 00:04:03,916
Instead it's heated with coals,
like it was in the old days.

55
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,750
It must be a great spot to work.

56
00:04:05,833 --> 00:04:07,250
I think I'll do some right now!

57
00:04:07,333 --> 00:04:08,541
I dunno.

58
00:04:08,625 --> 00:04:10,541
Every time I've tried
to work at a kotatsu,

59
00:04:10,625 --> 00:04:12,500
I ended up falling asleep.

60
00:04:12,583 --> 00:04:14,833
But not that quickly!

61
00:04:19,458 --> 00:04:23,583
Well, it's okay to have days
like this every once in a while.

62
00:04:28,666 --> 00:04:30,333
[TEACHER]
That's all for today's lessons.

63
00:04:30,416 --> 00:04:33,875
Make sure you review
at home, alright?

64
00:04:33,958 --> 00:04:35,208
Do you guys want to go with me

65
00:04:35,291 --> 00:04:37,166
to try that new bakery
that just opened?

66
00:04:37,250 --> 00:04:38,416
That's a great idea!

67
00:04:38,500 --> 00:04:39,666
The one on East Street?

68
00:04:39,750 --> 00:04:41,000
Yeah, let's all go!

69
00:04:41,083 --> 00:04:42,833
Um, hey, uh, can I come?

70
00:04:42,916 --> 00:04:44,041
[YOUNG QUEEN]
Okay, then it's set!

71
00:04:44,125 --> 00:04:45,500
Let's meet up
at the plaza later.

72
00:04:45,583 --> 00:04:47,750
--[GIRL 2] Sounds good!
--[GIRL 3] I can't wait!

73
00:04:47,833 --> 00:04:49,541
[GIRL 1]
Come on! Hurry up!

74
00:04:49,625 --> 00:04:51,583
[EPHERIA whimpers]

75
00:04:54,625 --> 00:04:56,208
[CHRISTINA, ALBERTINA sigh]

76
00:04:56,291 --> 00:04:58,375
[BOTH]
This is so warm and cozy.

77
00:04:58,458 --> 00:04:59,708
[knocking]

78
00:05:01,833 --> 00:05:03,875
I brought everyone
some refreshments.

79
00:05:03,958 --> 00:05:04,708
Hey, thanks.

80
00:05:04,791 --> 00:05:06,166
That's perfect timing.

81
00:05:06,250 --> 00:05:08,541
This would be a great
spot to take a break.

82
00:05:08,625 --> 00:05:10,125
Yeah, good idea.

83
00:05:10,208 --> 00:05:12,708
Here, Effy. Would you
like a snack, too?

84
00:05:12,791 --> 00:05:13,541
[EPHERIA gasps]

85
00:05:13,625 --> 00:05:15,625
I couldn't possibly, Master.

86
00:05:15,708 --> 00:05:18,041
After all, I'm in the middle
of working right now.

87
00:05:18,125 --> 00:05:19,958
[YUUTO] Well, I say
you can take a break.

88
00:05:20,041 --> 00:05:21,875
Besides, it's more fun
to relax together.

89
00:05:23,541 --> 00:05:25,666
--[EPHERIA gasps]
--Let's all take it easy!

90
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,666
[giggles]

91
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:32,041
So, how has school
been for you?

92
00:05:32,125 --> 00:05:33,833
Have you made any
cool new friends?

93
00:05:33,916 --> 00:05:35,458
[EPHERIA sighs]

94
00:05:35,541 --> 00:05:36,916
[EPHERIA]
Well, uh...

95
00:05:38,416 --> 00:05:40,833
Everyone in class
is really nice to me!

96
00:05:40,916 --> 00:05:44,541
I see. Is that so?

97
00:05:44,625 --> 00:05:46,375
[CHRISTINA] You're such
an overprotective parent.

98
00:05:46,458 --> 00:05:48,208
You know that, right, Father?

99
00:05:48,291 --> 00:05:49,500
While I don't really mind

100
00:05:49,583 --> 00:05:51,750
you using my rune
to conceal yourself.

101
00:05:51,833 --> 00:05:53,833
I don't agree with
you spying on her.

102
00:05:53,916 --> 00:05:55,708
Putting Effy in school
was my idea,

103
00:05:55,791 --> 00:05:57,791
and she's my responsibility.

104
00:05:57,875 --> 00:05:59,375
It's the right thing to do.

105
00:05:59,458 --> 00:06:00,708
Is it, though?

106
00:06:00,791 --> 00:06:03,541
So, what will you do if
Effy wants to get married?

107
00:06:03,625 --> 00:06:06,166
"Get your hands off
my daughter, vagrant!"

108
00:06:06,250 --> 00:06:09,166
I bet you'll wind up
pulling something like that.

109
00:06:09,250 --> 00:06:10,666
Hey look at this.

110
00:06:10,750 --> 00:06:12,791
Does it seem like the other
students are ignoring Effy?

111
00:06:12,875 --> 00:06:13,875
[YOUNG QUEEN]
My father brought home

112
00:06:13,958 --> 00:06:15,375
over 30 paper books!

113
00:06:15,458 --> 00:06:16,833
Now we have so many,

114
00:06:16,916 --> 00:06:18,500
we could probably
feed our goats with them

115
00:06:18,583 --> 00:06:20,208
--if we wanted to.
--Hey, uh...

116
00:06:21,583 --> 00:06:23,958
It really doesn't look like
anyone is bothering her to me.

117
00:06:24,041 --> 00:06:26,041
I would say being
ignored bothers her.

118
00:06:27,291 --> 00:06:29,166
I've got a great idea.

119
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:31,333
Instead of her father
barging in,

120
00:06:31,416 --> 00:06:34,541
why don't you just go ahead
and let me handle this?

121
00:06:36,166 --> 00:06:38,875
[TEACHER] Allow me to introduce
two new members of the class.

122
00:06:38,958 --> 00:06:41,541
Please meet Lady Christina
and Lady Albertina.

123
00:06:41,625 --> 00:06:43,000
They'll be studying
with you all.

124
00:06:43,083 --> 00:06:44,333
Let's give them a warm welcome.

125
00:06:44,416 --> 00:06:45,750
They what?

126
00:06:45,833 --> 00:06:46,958
[TEACHER]
Despite their young age,

127
00:06:47,041 --> 00:06:48,708
the two of them have
become oath daughters

128
00:06:48,791 --> 00:06:50,750
of our great
Patriarch Yuuto.

129
00:06:50,833 --> 00:06:53,708
Not only that, they're also
the blood daughters of Botvid,

130
00:06:53,791 --> 00:06:56,250
the Patriarch of our neighbors,
the Claw Clan.

131
00:06:56,333 --> 00:06:58,666
Everyone, please treat
them with respect.

132
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:01,416
Nice to meet you all!
Call me Albertina!

133
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:03,958
Al might be introducing herself
like a normal student,

134
00:07:04,041 --> 00:07:06,125
but she's only tagging
along with me today.

135
00:07:06,208 --> 00:07:07,291
You can just ignore her.

136
00:07:07,375 --> 00:07:09,958
Hey! I am too a normal student!

137
00:07:10,041 --> 00:07:11,500
How do you think you
can attend school

138
00:07:11,583 --> 00:07:12,916
when you don't even know how to

139
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:15,041
write your own name,
let alone read it?

140
00:07:15,125 --> 00:07:16,833
--I can read!
--[CHRISTINA] Really?

141
00:07:16,916 --> 00:07:20,000
Then tell me what this word is.

142
00:07:20,083 --> 00:07:21,666
I don't really know that one.

143
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:24,458
But I do know that it doesn't
say my name on there!

144
00:07:24,541 --> 00:07:26,083
See, I told you I could read!

145
00:07:26,166 --> 00:07:28,166
Huh. I guess it looks
like you might have learned

146
00:07:28,250 --> 00:07:29,791
how to read a thing
or two after all.

147
00:07:29,875 --> 00:07:31,875
But of course I did!

148
00:07:31,958 --> 00:07:34,625
Don't you underestimate
your older sister!

149
00:07:34,708 --> 00:07:36,166
[CHRISTINA] By the way,
that name I wrote down

150
00:07:36,250 --> 00:07:38,041
was the name of
our father, Botvid.

151
00:07:38,125 --> 00:07:39,291
Just so you know.

152
00:07:39,375 --> 00:07:42,250
I'm sorry, Father!
Please forgive me!

153
00:07:42,333 --> 00:07:43,708
Um, is she...

154
00:07:43,791 --> 00:07:45,958
We would like to take
our seats now.

155
00:07:46,041 --> 00:07:48,916
Ah! Give us the
ones next to Effy!

156
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:49,916
We know her.

157
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:52,875
She lives with us in the palace.

158
00:07:52,958 --> 00:07:53,625
What?

159
00:07:53,708 --> 00:07:54,875
[EPHERIA yelps]

160
00:07:54,958 --> 00:07:56,458
Effy.

161
00:07:56,541 --> 00:07:59,500
Al and I would appreciate it if
you'd go get us some tablets.

162
00:07:59,583 --> 00:08:00,791
Uh, yes! Right away!

163
00:08:00,875 --> 00:08:02,166
And a glass of water as well.

164
00:08:02,250 --> 00:08:04,666
I'm starting to get
a bit thirsty.

165
00:08:04,750 --> 00:08:06,000
Sure!

166
00:08:06,083 --> 00:08:07,750
[CHRISTINA] Effy. My shoulders
are feeling stiff.

167
00:08:07,833 --> 00:08:10,166
--Would you massage them?
--[EPHERIA] Okay!

168
00:08:10,250 --> 00:08:12,083
--[CHRISTINA] And also--
--[ALBERTINA] Oh! I can do it!

169
00:08:12,166 --> 00:08:15,166
--[CHRISTINA] You be quiet.
--[YOUNG QUEEN growls]

170
00:08:15,250 --> 00:08:18,041
[CHRISTINA] That classroom is
being ruled by a little queen.

171
00:08:18,125 --> 00:08:19,375
What?

172
00:08:19,458 --> 00:08:20,791
[CHRISTINA] She's the one
that's been telling

173
00:08:20,875 --> 00:08:23,958
all of the other girls
in class to ignore Effy.

174
00:08:24,041 --> 00:08:25,875
But why would someone do that?

175
00:08:25,958 --> 00:08:28,041
This is all your fault, Father!

176
00:08:28,125 --> 00:08:29,333
Why me?

177
00:08:29,416 --> 00:08:31,666
When Effy was enrolled
at that school,

178
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:33,875
you accompanied her
on the very first day,

179
00:08:33,958 --> 00:08:36,375
and then proceeded to act
especially close with her,

180
00:08:36,458 --> 00:08:37,541
isn't that right?

181
00:08:37,625 --> 00:08:39,291
I guess I gave her
some special treatment,

182
00:08:39,375 --> 00:08:40,458
but that's only
because I figured

183
00:08:40,541 --> 00:08:42,000
it would help her fit in.

184
00:08:42,083 --> 00:08:43,916
You really don't understand
a single thing

185
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,500
about how women think, do you?

186
00:08:45,583 --> 00:08:47,125
It's practically laughable.

187
00:08:47,208 --> 00:08:49,125
[YUUTO]
Wait. What do you mean?

188
00:08:49,208 --> 00:08:52,208
It's a case of female jealousy.

189
00:08:52,291 --> 00:08:54,250
Every girl in that class
obviously wanted you

190
00:08:54,333 --> 00:08:56,375
to pay attention to them
when you showed up.

191
00:08:56,458 --> 00:08:58,291
But you clearly only
cared about Effy,

192
00:08:58,375 --> 00:08:59,916
so of course
they got jealous.

193
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:02,750
That little queen in particular.

194
00:09:02,833 --> 00:09:04,500
[YUUTO groans]

195
00:09:04,583 --> 00:09:06,208
[sighs]

196
00:09:06,291 --> 00:09:08,416
So, what do we do about it?

197
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:10,541
[CHRISTINA] Sit back and
watch while I rise to power

198
00:09:10,625 --> 00:09:13,000
and become the new
queen of the classroom.

199
00:09:13,083 --> 00:09:14,708
Okay?

200
00:09:14,791 --> 00:09:16,583
[CHRISTINA] After I
establish myself as such,

201
00:09:16,666 --> 00:09:19,208
I'll be able to bolster Effy's
standing in the class.

202
00:09:19,291 --> 00:09:20,916
As a close companion
of the queen,

203
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,791
no one will be able
to ignore her.

204
00:09:22,875 --> 00:09:24,875
Simple, yet ingenious.

205
00:09:24,958 --> 00:09:27,333
[YUUTO]
Hmm. Now I get it.

206
00:09:27,416 --> 00:09:28,833
Just relax, Father.

207
00:09:28,916 --> 00:09:30,416
Leave it to me.

208
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:33,583
I'll make sure that everything
goes according to plan.

209
00:09:34,916 --> 00:09:36,833
[TEACHER]
That's all for today's lessons.

210
00:09:36,916 --> 00:09:40,666
Hey so, you want to come
over to my house later?

211
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:42,666
Huh?

212
00:09:42,750 --> 00:09:43,958
[GIRL 2]
Lady Christina,

213
00:09:44,041 --> 00:09:46,041
do you have any
plans for us today?

214
00:09:46,125 --> 00:09:47,583
I do.

215
00:09:47,666 --> 00:09:49,666
I was thinking we could all take
a trip to the bath together.

216
00:09:49,750 --> 00:09:51,958
Father asked me to check out
this particular location

217
00:09:52,041 --> 00:09:53,791
and report back with
my thoughts about it.

218
00:09:53,875 --> 00:09:55,166
I asked him if I
could bring along

219
00:09:55,250 --> 00:09:57,291
some of my friends
from school with me.

220
00:09:57,375 --> 00:10:00,208
He said it was no problem,
so you're all welcome to join!

221
00:10:00,291 --> 00:10:02,416
Wow, do you really mean it,
Lady Christina?

222
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:03,958
[GIRL 1]
Wonderful!

223
00:10:04,041 --> 00:10:07,833
We're so lucky to be friends
with someone as generous as you!

224
00:10:07,916 --> 00:10:09,958
Alright then,
let's get going, everybody.

225
00:10:10,041 --> 00:10:11,291
[GIRLS]
Okay!

226
00:10:13,083 --> 00:10:15,166
Aren't you gonna go with them?

227
00:10:15,250 --> 00:10:16,791
Hey, did you hear what I said?

228
00:10:16,875 --> 00:10:19,166
--[EPHERIA grunts]
--Huh?

229
00:10:20,875 --> 00:10:22,333
[gasps]

230
00:10:24,083 --> 00:10:26,750
[YOUNG QUEEN]
Uh...

231
00:10:26,833 --> 00:10:29,041
--What's this?
--An invitation!

232
00:10:29,125 --> 00:10:30,833
[YOUNG QUEEN growls]

233
00:10:30,916 --> 00:10:32,875
I don't need any
sympathy from you.

234
00:10:32,958 --> 00:10:34,875
Just go away and leave me alone.

235
00:10:34,958 --> 00:10:36,708
Huh?

236
00:10:36,791 --> 00:10:38,375
[whines softly]

237
00:10:45,375 --> 00:10:46,125
[determined grunt]

238
00:10:46,208 --> 00:10:47,625
-Listen!
-[YOUNG QUEEN] Hm?

239
00:10:47,708 --> 00:10:50,041
I thought I already told you no!

240
00:10:50,125 --> 00:10:52,250
I'd really like you
to come with us!

241
00:10:52,333 --> 00:10:53,958
Did you hear a word I said?

242
00:10:54,041 --> 00:10:55,916
--[EPHERIA] I heard you.
--[gasps]

243
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:58,416
It's just everyone
has a lot more fun

244
00:10:58,500 --> 00:11:00,958
when all of our
friends are together!

245
00:11:02,458 --> 00:11:03,875
[EPHERIA]
Mm-hm.

246
00:11:09,833 --> 00:11:11,250
[EPHERIA]
Let's go.

247
00:11:21,666 --> 00:11:24,166
I have resolved Effy's issue,
just like I said I would.

248
00:11:24,250 --> 00:11:25,708
That's good to hear!

249
00:11:25,791 --> 00:11:28,208
So, I guess that means your
time as students is over then?

250
00:11:28,291 --> 00:11:31,291
Yes, all over!

251
00:11:31,375 --> 00:11:31,833
Huh?

252
00:11:31,916 --> 00:11:32,958
Not just yet.

253
