Come on.

507
00:20:36,791 --> 00:20:38,541
You don't really
mean that do you?

508
00:20:38,625 --> 00:20:40,541
Are you actually okay with
spending your whole life

509
00:20:40,625 --> 00:20:41,500
stuck in a forge?

510
00:20:41,583 --> 00:20:42,708
It's fine by me!

511
00:20:45,166 --> 00:20:46,916
I've already gotten what I want.

512
00:20:48,458 --> 00:20:49,708
Thanks for this, Yuuto.

513
00:20:49,791 --> 00:20:51,750
I think it'll help
my motivation.

514
00:20:51,833 --> 00:20:53,000
Good to hear.

515
00:20:53,083 --> 00:20:53,750
[INGRID chuckles]

516
00:20:53,833 --> 00:20:55,375
[YUUTO]
Work hard, okay?

517
00:21:05,041 --> 00:21:06,125
[LOPTR]
Enlighten me.

518
00:21:06,208 --> 00:21:07,208
What exactly sparked

519
00:21:07,291 --> 00:21:09,291
the Empire's interest
in all of this?

520
00:21:09,375 --> 00:21:10,708
It is the duty of the Empire

521
00:21:10,791 --> 00:21:13,916
to ensure that order is
maintained all across the land.

522
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:15,250
And it seems the Wolf Clan

523
00:21:15,333 --> 00:21:17,625
has been disrupting
that order as of late.

524
00:21:17,708 --> 00:21:19,208
What's your point?

525
00:21:19,291 --> 00:21:20,500
There are no current
ties between

526
00:21:20,583 --> 00:21:22,000
the Lightning
and Panther clans.

527
00:21:22,083 --> 00:21:24,541
And yet you're proposing
an Oath of the Chalice?

528
00:21:26,375 --> 00:21:28,333
Let's say that we do
take this oath.

529
00:21:28,416 --> 00:21:31,208
Would I be the younger,
or the elder?

530
00:21:31,291 --> 00:21:33,375
[ALEXIS] You must consider
the Lightning Clan's position

531
00:21:33,458 --> 00:21:34,625
in this as well.

532
00:21:34,708 --> 00:21:36,416
Why not brothers
of equal standing?

533
00:21:36,500 --> 00:21:37,375
Equal standing?

534
00:21:37,458 --> 00:21:39,208
I accept.

535
00:21:40,458 --> 00:21:43,916
I'm not interested in
any more younger brothers.

536
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:45,708
That's very good to hear.

537
00:21:45,791 --> 00:21:48,041
Then shall I proceed
with the plan?

538
00:21:48,125 --> 00:21:49,041
You shall.

539
00:21:49,125 --> 00:21:52,291
Best of luck to you,
Lord Alexis.

540
00:21:55,041 --> 00:21:56,666
[ALEXIS]
Of course.

541
00:21:56,750 --> 00:21:59,166
Let us make the young
Patriarch of the Wolf Clan

542
00:21:59,250 --> 00:22:01,958
disappear from
this world forever.

543
00:23:32,625 --> 00:23:33,625
There were quite a few kids

544
00:23:33,708 --> 00:23:35,125
in this episode,
don't you think?

545
00:23:35,208 --> 00:23:36,875
I just hope some of them
are interested in smithing.

546
00:23:36,958 --> 00:23:38,375
Or I can make
Al my apprentice.

547
00:23:38,458 --> 00:23:40,333
--Why would you?
--She's cute and obedient.

548
00:23:40,416 --> 00:23:42,125
--She'd make a great smith.
--[CHRISTINA groans]

549
00:23:42,208 --> 00:23:44,458
Maybe I should start training
her as soon as possible!

550
00:23:44,541 --> 00:23:46,958
You and I need to
have a little chat.

